            <div class="title">
                British Army (New Rifle)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1954-02-01/debates/4ceb2b29-012b-4740-8b4d-7ad8e3e77900/HillFarmingBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
