<p class=""><em>indicated dissent</em>.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f764b05c-ea1a-43ff-9c22-fb76c05f0d1b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
