                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-769bf1ad-9640-4ef9-a783-2eed7f209c18" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
